We also share your account details, so insurance partners can pay you if you make a successful insurance claim. We share your payment details too, so we can collect payments you owe us for using lounge access benefits. Our legal basis for sharing your information for these reasons is contractual necessity: we need to use your data for a contract we have with you. To learn how our partners use your information, please see their privacy notice‚Äôs below.
