Other Monzo Group companies
We may share details about you with other Monzo companies for reasons explained in the ‚ÄòOur reasons for using your information‚Äô section. We may share your details with people or companies if we change the structure of our group of companies, merge with another company, or get bought by another company.
How long we keep your information üìÅ
We‚Äôll keep your information for 6 years in case we need to respond to a legal claim. In some circumstances, like cases of anti-money laundering or fraud, we may keep data longer if we need to (that‚Äôs in our legitimate interest) and/or the law says we have to.
To work out how long we keep different categories of data, we consider why we hold it, how sensitive it is, how long the law says we need to keep it for, and what the risks are.
